Package: FinCovRegularization
Type: Package
Title: Covariance Matrix Estimation and Regularization for Finance
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Yachen", "Yan", email = "yanyachen21@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is a package providing three categories of important functions for statistical analysis of financial data: 
    including portfolio optimization: global mimnum variance portfolio, risk parity portfolio; 
    covariance estimation: through macroeconomic, fundamental, and statistical factor model; 
    and covariance regularization: banding, tapering, thresholding and corresponding cross-validation for parameter selection. 
URL: http://github.com/yanyachen/FinCovRegularization
BugReports: http://github.com/yanyachen/FinCovRegularization/issues
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: quadprog
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Packaged: 2015-02-27 03:36:17 UTC; Administrator
Author: Yachen Yan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yachen Yan <yanyachen21@gmail.com>
